        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Does Happy Roof handle commercial roof maintenance and inspections?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Happy Roof offers commercial roof inspection and maintenance programs for Tampa Bay property managers and business owners. Regular inspections identify small issues before they become expensive problems, extending the life of your commercial roof system. Contact us for a maintenance proposal." }
