      </div>
      <div class="scard p-7">
        <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F5B800" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Maintenance Programs</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We offer ongoing maintenance and inspection programs to extend the life of your commercial roof. Catch small problems before they become expensive repairs.</p></div></div>
