    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Site Assessment & Proposal</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We conduct a thorough assessment of your commercial roof, including core samples if needed, drainage evaluation, and structural review. You receive a detailed proposal with system options, material specifications, project timeline, and pricing. No pressure, no hidden costs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">System Design & Permitting</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Once scope is approved, we finalize the system design, order materials directly from the manufacturer, and pull all required building permits. We coordinate with your property manager or facilities team to establish a work schedule that minimizes impact on your operations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our licensed crews perform the full installation - tear-off, deck repair, insulation, membrane or panel installation, and flashing details. We maintain a clean, safe job site throughout the project and provide daily progress updates. All work is performed to manufacturer specifications and local building codes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Inspection, Warranty & Follow-Up</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">After installation, we schedule the county inspection and ensure code compliance. You receive complete warranty documentation - our workmanship warranty plus manufacturer material warranty. We conduct a 30-day follow-up inspection and can set up an ongoing maintenance schedule to protect your investment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

