      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides commercial roofing services across Hillsborough, Pinellas, and Pasco counties. Wherever your business is in Tampa Bay, we've got you covered.</p>
